[2], 21 [i.e. 29], [1] p. : ill.
Are to be sould, by Thomas Ienner, in his shop at the old Exhange, [London] : [1646]
Signed at the foot of page 21 [i.e. 29]: Collected by John Vicars. A1r is blank. Title and imprint from engraving on A1v; place and date of publication from Wing. Page 29 is misnumbered 21. Annotation on Thomason copy, leaf A1r: "Decemb: 5th Lond: 1646". Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
